The paper presents an interactive visualisation tool for recommending travel trajectories, which involves machine learning formulations and algorithms for the trajectory recommendation problem. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC) for the interactive visualisation aspect, Information Retrieval (cs.IR) for the recommendation problem, Machine Learning (cs.LG) for the machine learning formulations and algorithms, Databases (cs.DB) for the data management aspect, and Graphics (cs.GR) for the visualisation techniques used.
